Class PageRankString

  • java.lang.Object
    • PageRankString

  • public class PageRankString
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to compute the page rank of node/pages of a web graph. Due to the specification of the assignment, this class deals with the web graph as Strings. The real PageRank class simply proxies the methods exposed here and translates the results into the appropriate types.
